{"tid":184479,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒燶車位】沙田河畔花園連環兩撻定 殺定20.6萬","createTime":"2017-04-02T23:34:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T04:21:15.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5e43c01208bf881e8d2c2bd7bce633bbf5eb323d","tid":184479,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T23:34:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/03/073414_b493ba016af67118557a9ff98247b52a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F03%2F073414_b493ba016af67118557a9ff98247b52a.jpg&h=d4870152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年底政府加辣後，資金流向非住宅市場，車位熱潮乍現，結果車位炒燶輸鑊甘。資深投資者蔡伯能拆售的沙田河畔花園停車場首錄撻大定個案，兩名投資者分別輸9.8萬元及10.8萬元，比起去年底東涌怒火師奶疑輸細定狂炳代理，輸得更多。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料，沙田河畔花園停車場兩個車位買家均姓黃，去年12月底分別以98萬元及108萬元購入一個車位，已經去到支付大定階段，分別支付9.8萬元及10.8萬元定金，然而上月底撤銷買賣合約，合共20.6萬元定金被殺。<br />\n<br />\n資深投資者蔡伯能2015年以約8,115.9萬元向恒地(012)買入上述停車場，其後拆售初期反應欠佳，直至去年年底政府加辣後加佣促銷，私家車位售價約80萬至115萬元，貨車位每個售168萬元，結果全部車位4日內沽清。去年底東涌映灣園一名怒火師奶疑買入河畔花園及太和中心合共3個車位，因摩不出貨，衝入代理行連環拳擊經紀出氣，據悉3個車位合共輸細定9萬元。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經生活資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=721c0ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56514511&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56514511%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170402&d=0fPPgjUU32Qc%2B%2Bj2t4ropB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=1b8c425d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56514511%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170402&h=5407d5fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56514511&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170402</a>"},{"pid":"44b6ff1a3549c9328fe660c61d0dfdebfe976b59","tid":184479,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T23:52:55.000Z","msg":"連環拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82dd65c68ac5b705e26a2b5a1c1e1e4227ea26d4","tid":184479,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:00:17.000Z","msg":"c9諗住落訂1星期內有人接貨，冇人接硬食上會冇錢就瀨嘢，車位要比6成，幾十萬比唔起學人炒輸到甩轆"},{"pid":"99746d8fdc1837308a02ba93b448083d50a6f575","tid":184479,"uid":21310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:03:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ce42865eebb73859d7e09cbcdef9c2764cd41d77","tid":184479,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T00:07:57.000Z","msg":"咁容易摸貨，個AA自己買啦，洗鬼益佢咩！不過似係比AA呃，寶藥黨之類既手法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b474fae9b7a2a0ceeb1d51273384461f642d63","tid":184479,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T04:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁容易摸貨，個AA自己買啦，洗鬼益佢咩！不過似係比AA呃，寶藥黨之類既手法！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n抵撚死屌你老母乜都拎黎炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}